title: Seattle Grunge Scene and Other Stuff
description:
Dr. Kirk nerds out about the Seattle grunge scene with Brendon Mendoza - mental health counselor and former music industry figure.

Become a patron of our podcast by going to https://www.patreon.com/PsychologyInSeattle
